									<a href="http://www.nytimes.com/adx/bin/adx_click.html?type=goto&amp;page=www.nytimes.com/archive/article/sports&amp;pos=Frame4A&amp;sn2=aa2d0a79/cfa7a29a&amp;sn1=91ea2d57/c0f453b&amp;camp=foxsearch2009_emailtools_1011072c_nyt5&amp;ad=500DOS_120x60_c&amp;goto=http://www.foxsearchlight.com/500daysofsummer" target="_blank">
<img src="magicEndsCareer_files/article-sponsor.gif" class="label" alt="Article Tools Sponsored By" width="62" border="0" height="20"><img src="magicEndsCareer_files/500days_nytimes_120x60_looping.gif" alt="" width="120" border="0" height="60"></a>	
